          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Public Input for National Monuments Act</b></p> <p>This bill applies the National Environmental Policy Act of 1969 to the designation of a national monument. The President must certify compliance with the Act when designating national monuments.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2017-04-06T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
